# ─── RouteSim: MUST KEEP (prebuilt FFI — required for CI) ───────────────────
# Do NOT add rules that ignore *.a or StikDebug/idevice/
# The following are intentionally tracked:
#   StikDebug/idevice/libidevice_ffi.a  (~97 MB)
#   StikDebug/idevice/idevice.h
#   StikDebug/idevice/module.modulemap

